snippet.textDisplay:
I waited for her more than 5 years, then from last year (2023) we’re dating. And now after almost a year she started ghosting me , avoiding to talk. It all ended with a “mann nehi hai” .Its all the outgoings, 100s of bike rides, movies together, dinners, night outs, and trips from Bangalore. Now the whole city have our memories. Each and every place with her i remember every seconds of us. I get flashbacks on the line 

“Jaaunga kahan mai toh hu yaha, tere dil ki ahtoon mai hoon
Sapnoo mai tu soch mai tu, har lamhe mai hai tu”
